            "answer_text": "My husband is playing harmonica for past 10 yrs and he is founder member of Bangalore Harmonica Club. There are different kinds of harmonicas with different scales.  According to him, Hohner is the best harmonica. To play melody songs, you can use super chromonica.  For English melody, you can use blues harmonica.  If you are a beginner, you can start with Suzuki song star for chromatic and Silver Star for Blues as they are less expensive. Hope this information is of help. ",
